<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<section class="section" style="padding-bottom: 80px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Frequently Asked Questions</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to know.</h2>
    </div>
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What is Cloud HQ?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Cloud HQ (Cloud Headquarters) is Teamwork Commerce's enterprise reporting and analytics platform. Analytics is part of Teamwork Commerce Services, extending the same Mobile POS you already run — it turns transaction, RFID, and mPOS data into 150+ pre-configured reports covering sales, inventory, associate performance, fulfillment, compliance, and more, accessible from a single global dashboard with real-time multi-currency support across 40+ countries. It's simply included with your deployment — no separate purchase or upgrade tier.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          How does the AI insight engine work?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>The Natural Language Interface lets you ask questions in plain English. The AI cross-references multiple data sources — sales data, RFID inventory, weather, staffing schedules, and promotional calendars — to identify root causes and recommend actions. Predictive forecasting uses machine learning to project demand by SKU and location with up to 95% accuracy.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What RFID-specific analytics are available?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>RFID analytics include fitting room conversion tracking (items tried vs. purchased), path-to-purchase heatmaps showing product movement through the store, tag velocity monitoring for demand prediction, dead zone and hot zone identification, and stock-out prevention alerts. These physical-world analytics are impossible with barcode-only systems.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          Can I create custom reports and dashboards?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Beyond the 150+ pre-configured reports, Cloud HQ supports fully custom dashboards, scheduled report generation, and on-demand report building. Business users get one-click summaries while IT teams get granular data access. Reports can be tailored by vertical — from high-volume sporting goods to luxury fashion to museum retail.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          Does Cloud HQ support multi-currency and localized tax reporting?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. View global GMV in your base currency while the system handles exchange rate fluctuations for every market. Localized tax reporting auto-generates VAT summaries for the EU, GST for APAC, and State/Local Sales Tax for the US — ensuring compliance is built into every report, not bolted on after.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

